author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
I've been away so I missed the Benson Boone brouhaha surrounding Brian May's reception at Coachella. However, I was kept updated by a younger member of the Hawkins family who had thoughts. So today I'm sharing those and some of my own....
